{"data": [{"id": "4742885", "title": "Wall Street Week Ahead", "description": "<div class=\"wsb_wrapper\"> <div class=\"wsb_main\"><span><p class=\"wsb_pb\"><strong>Listen on the go! A daily podcast of Wall Street Breakfast will be available by 8:00 a.m. on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/wall-street-breakfast?utm_source=newsletter&amp;utm_medium=toptext&amp;utm_campaign=wsbpodpromo\">Seeking Alpha</a>, <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502\" rel=\"nofollow\">iTunes</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a>.</strong></p></span></div> <figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img alt=\"\" data-id=\"2171438579\" data-type=\"getty-image\" height=\"864px\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" width=\"1536px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sila Damrongsaringkan/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></picture></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div>\n<div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\">The Fed pendulum swings back to the inflation part of the mandate this week. The November consumer price index hits on Wednesday, just a week before the FOMC's final 2024 meeting.<br><br>Economists expect that headline and core CPI, which excludes food and energy, rose 0.3% last month. In addition, the headline producer price index, which is due Thursday, rose 0.3%, with the core PPI up 0.2%.<br><br>Last week's November payrolls was a Goldilocks number for those hoping for a December rate cut: solid, but not enough to derail the Fed's easing path. The odds of a quarter-point cut rose to 86%.<br><br>Among the big names reporting earnings this week are Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Adobe (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a>), Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>), Costco Wholesale (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COST\" title=\"Costco Wholesale Corporation\">COST</a>), Toll Brothers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a>) and Ciena (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIEN\" title=\"Ciena Corporation\">CIEN</a>).<br><br>The Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference starts Tuesday and the Barclays 22nd Annual Global Technology Conference begins Wednesday.</p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p class=\"wsp-pb\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Earnings spotlight:</strong> Monday, December 9 - Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Toll Brothers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a>), and Casey\u2019s General Stores (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CASY\" title=\"Casey's General Stores, Inc.\">CASY</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><strong>Earnings spotlight:</strong> Tuesday, December 10 - AutoZone (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AZO\" title=\"AutoZone, Inc.\">AZO</a>), Ferguson Enterprises (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FERG\" title=\"Ferguson Enterprises Inc.\">FERG</a>), GameStop (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GME\" title=\"GameStop Corp.\">GME</a>), Ollie\u2019s Bargain Outlet Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OLLI\" title=\"Ollie's Bargain Outlet Holdings, Inc.\">OLLI</a>), and Academy Sports and Outdoors (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASO\" title=\"Academy Sports and Outdoors, Inc.\">ASO</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><strong>Earnings spotlight: </strong>Wednesday, December 11 - Adobe (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.<br><br><strong>Earnings spotlight:</strong> Thursday, December 12 - Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>), Costco Wholesale (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COST\" title=\"Costco Wholesale Corporation\">COST</a>), and Ciena (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIEN\" title=\"Ciena Corporation\">CIEN</a>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">See the full earnings calendar</a>.</p> </div></div> <div class=\"wsb_section\"><div class=\"wsb_mb\"> <p class=\"wsb_bold\">In Case You Missed It ...</p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div>\n<p class=\"wsp-pb\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362670-markets-stocks-why-you-should-be-checking-reddit-again-ahead-of-trading-meme\">Why you should be checking Reddit again ahead of trading</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4371397-wells-fargos-core-list-googl-dis-hd-wmt-and-more\">Wells Fargo\u2019s \u2018Core\u2019 List</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4359652-15-high-flyer-stocks-that-have-soared-over-100-in-2024-that-still-offer-potential-growth\">15 high flyers that still look cheap</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4367388-11-compounder-opportunities-according-to-goldman-amd-bdx-infa\">11 Compounder opportunities according to Goldman</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4359851-top-quant-rated-cyclical-stocks-as-group-is-expected-to-outperform-in-2025\">Top quant-rated cyclical stocks, as group is expected to outperform in 2025</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4360726-the-top-20-technology-stocks-ranked-by-quant\">Top 20 Technology stocks ranked by Quant</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4365097-what-seeking-alpha-analysts-are-saying-as-bitcoin-trades-above-100000\">What Seeking Alpha analysts are saying as Bitcoin trades above $100K</a><br><br><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4354286-marjorie-taylor-greene-discloses-buys-of-amd-alphabet-microsoft-others\">Marjorie Taylor Greene discloses buys of AMD, Alphabet, Microsoft, others</a></p> </div></div> <div class=\"wsb_pt\"> </div> </div>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171438579/image_2171438579.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742885-wall-street-week-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 15:04:07"}, {"id": "4742874", "title": "Tempus AI: Why I'm Buying This AI Stock", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Using AI technology helps with genetic code prediction research.\" data-id=\"1728138175\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Suriphon Singha</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Tempus AI is one of the biggest AI health tech players in the US, with 200+ biopharma partners and over <a href=\"https://investors.tempus.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://investors.tempus.com/\" target=\"_blank\">half of US oncologists</a> connected to it via partnerships, well positioned to grasp a piece of the cake in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1728138175/image_1728138175.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742874-tempus-ai-why-im-buying-this-ai-stock", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:56:58"}, {"id": "4742871", "title": "Laurentian Bank: But Maybe We Will Be TD", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"LBC Capital headquarters building in Burlington.\" data-id=\"1272312669\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em><strong>Note: All amounts discussed are in Canadian Dollars and the stock price refers to the TSX stock price and not the OTC one.</strong></em></p> <p>In our last coverage of Laurentian Bank (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LRCDF\" title=\"Laurentian Bank of Canada\">OTCPK:LRCDF</a>)(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LB:CA\" title=\"Laurentian Bank of Canada\">LB:CA</a></span>), we gave our own</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1272312669/image_1272312669.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742871-laurentian-bank-maybe-we-will-be-td", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:43:24"}, {"id": "4742870", "title": "JEPI: Macroeconomic Volatility Could Help Performance In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Team businesspeople or an accountant team are analyzing data charts, graphs, and a dashboard on a laptop screen in order to prepare a statistical report and discuss financial data in an office.\" data-id=\"1705145695\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">David Gyung</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The<strong> JPMorgan Equity Premium Income ETF</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JEPI\" title=\"JPMorgan Equity Premium Income ETF\">JEPI</a></span>) is an exchange-traded fund which seeks to capitalize from long-term appreciation of the stock market while also offering a generous monthly dividend yield. In theory, if executed well, this could</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705145695/image_1705145695.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742870-jepi-macroeconomic-volatility-could-help-performance-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:30:25"}, {"id": "4742868", "title": "Salesforce Is Fairly Valued Now (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Artificial Intelligence Machine Learning Large Language Model Technology\" data-id=\"2161221488\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"960px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Just_Super/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of Salesforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM\" title=\"Salesforce, Inc.\">CRM</a></span>) surged 11% after the CRM applications provider submitted a better than expected earnings sheet (in terms of revenue) for the third fiscal quarter. Salesforce beat top line estimates by a wide margin and is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2161221488/image_2161221488.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742868-salesforce-is-fairly-valued-now-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:23:14"}, {"id": "4742830", "title": "The Stock Market Has Entered The Danger Zone", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Warning Danger Zone red signage in forest.\" data-id=\"637778526\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1405px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">junce</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The stock market has reached one of those moments when <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742300-most-expensive-stock-market-ever\">valuations</a> and mechanics have reached dangerous levels. The last time this happened was in July, when implied correlations were trading at very low levels as realized volatility had melted.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/637778526/image_637778526.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742830-stock-market-entered-danger-zone", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:15:00"}, {"id": "4742866", "title": "IBM Is In The Midst Of An AI Renaissance - Stop Doubting That", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Advancing Technology\" data-id=\"1096528616\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"768px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">kentoh/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>For the first time in decades, IBM (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBM\" title=\"International Business Machines Corporation\">IBM</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IBM:CA\" title=\"International Business Machines Corporation\">IBM:CA</a></span>) is expected to close out 2024 beating the S&amp;P 500 index. This is a data point that is most likely expected to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1096528616/image_1096528616.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742866-ibm-is-in-the-midst-of-an-ai-renaissance-stop-doubting-that", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 14:06:19"}, {"id": "4742865", "title": "Meta's AI CAPEX Fears, Regulatory Concerns Are Overblown", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Meta European head office\" data-id=\"1359152239\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1088px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Derick Hudson</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>Introduction &amp; Investment Thesis</span></h2> <p>I<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722231-meta-platforms-stock-gains-from-tiktoks-pains\"> last wrote</a> about Meta (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/META\" title=\"Meta Platforms, Inc.\">META</a></span>) in September, where I valued the business as a sum of its two parts, 1) Family of Apps (FoA) and 2) Reality Labs, and decided that the stock is a \u201cbuy\u201d with a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359152239/image_1359152239.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742865-metas-ai-capex-fears-regulatory-concerns-overblown", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 13:38:06"}, {"id": "4742864", "title": "Project $1M: End Of A Journey With Mission Accomplished", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"1 Million Celebration Balloons with Confetti\" data-id=\"1401505902\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">asbe</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>A little over 9 years ago, I started a tracked portfolio on Seeking Alpha with the objective of turning a fixed sum of approximately <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/3668026-introducing-project-1m-achieving-1m-growth-stocks\">$275k into $1M</a> over a period of 10 years. The aim of this portfolio was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1401505902/image_1401505902.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742864-project-1m-end-of-a-journey-with-mission-accomplished", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 13:28:55"}, {"id": "4742678", "title": "Alpha Picks Weekly Market Recap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"SUMMARY - a word written in a notebook on a pink background and colored pencils\" data-id=\"1691487492\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"950px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Zhanna Hapanovich/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>U.S. Tightens China Chip Ban</h2> <p>On Monday, the Biden administration announced its latest <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353387-us-puts-new-restrictions-on-chinas-access-to-ai-chips-tools\">technology restrictions</a> targeting China, marking the third major update in three years. This move aims to curtail China\u2019s access to advanced chips that<span class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"> play a crucial role in military equipment and artificial intelligence. The new rules prohibit the sale of specific advanced memory chips and about two dozen types of chip-manufacturing equipment to China. The Chinese Foreign Ministry expressed firm opposition to what it called \u2018economic coercion.\u2019</span></p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">This development represents yet another escalation in the ongoing tech rivalry between the U.S. and China, with potential long-term implications for global supply chains and the semiconductor industry. As the week progressed, markets continued to digest these changes, with the semiconductor sector showing resilience in the face of these new geopolitical changes. This announcement brought a <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/02/business/economy/biden-china-chips-exports.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">broad positive reaction</a> from U.S. and Japanese semiconductor companies. Stocks such as Applied Materials (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMAT\" title=\"Applied Materials, Inc.\">AMAT</a>), KLA Corporation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KLAC\" title=\"KLA Corporation\">KLAC</a>), and Lam Research (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LRCX\" title=\"Lam Research Corporation\">LRCX</a>) saw gains as investors interpreted the news as benefiting non-Chinese firms and redirecting global demand.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">In a separate but simultaneous development in the chip world, Intel (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a>) CEO Pat Gelsinger was <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4360501-chips-mixed-as-investors-digest-intel-ceo-departure-await-marvell-earnings\">driven out</a> by the board due to disappointing performance and a failure to regain market share from competitors like NVIDIA. Following the announcement of Gelsinger\u2019s departure, Intel\u2019s shares fell 5% as investors speculated on the direction under new leadership.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">If you're looking for a tool that simplifies stock picking by analyzing financial data to highlight stocks with the strongest investment fundamentals, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/alpha-picks/subscribe\">Alpha Picks</a> offers a more efficient approach to smarter investing. Alpha Picks leverages Seeking Alpha's powerful quantitative stock-picking system, delivering two data-driven stock picks each month, helping investors save time and focus on high-quality opportunities.</p> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Geopolitical Events: South Korea\u2019s Impeachment Proceedings</h2> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">The South Korean parliament moved towards impeaching President Yoon Suk Yeol after he unexpectedly <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4359443-south-korean-won-plummets-against-the-us-dollar-after-president-declares-emergency\">declared martial law</a> on Tuesday evening. Yoon\u2019s justification for martial law included accusations that the opposition party harbored sympathies for North Korea. The declaration of martial law was brief, lasting only a few hours before it was retracted, though the event was widely viewed as an overreach of presidential power. This event has led to impeachment proceedings against the president, highlighting the political instability within the country.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">The political turmoil had an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362416-south-korea-stocks-political-chaos-martial-law-reversed\">immediate impact</a> on South Korea\u2019s financial markets. The KOSPI index closed down 1.44% on Wednesday, while the South Korean won hit a new two-year low against the U.S. dollar before partially recovering. Stocks of several South Korean companies listed in the U.S. fell following the initial announcement. The iShares MSCI South Korea ETF (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EWY\" title=\"iShares MSCI South Korea Capped ETF\">EWY</a>), which tracks over 90 mid- and large-cap South Korean stocks, initially fell by 7% on Wednesday.</p> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">GICS Sector Performance</h2> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">This week, the technology sector rallied, with notable gains seen in chip stocks like NVIDIA (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>), which reacted positively to anticipated policy changes regarding semiconductor exports to China. The Consumer Discretionary (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XLY\" title=\"Consumer Discretionary Select Sector SPDR\u00ae Fund ETF\">XLY</a>) sector gained another 3.6% following robust consumer spending during the Black Friday weekend. Overall retail sales on Black Friday showed a 3.4% <a href=\"https://www.convenience.org/Media/Daily/2024/December/3/2-Retailers-Have-Successful-Black-Friday_Ops\" rel=\"nofollow\">increase</a> compared to the previous year.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><strong>Consumer Discretionary (XLY) remains the sector with the best 1-month performance</strong></p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_1924ebc1b22fb13134d3fc01e704f88b.png\" alt=\"US Equity Sector Performance\" contenteditable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span>Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure></p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">In contrast, defensive sectors such as Consumer Staples and Utilities lagged, reflecting a shift in investor sentiment toward growth-oriented stocks. The Energy sector also finished lower, as hopes for stronger demand prompted by higher factory activity in China were offset by concerns that the U.S. Federal Reserve will not cut interest rates again at its December meeting.</p> <h3 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Value vs. Growth</h3> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Growth stocks continued to outperform their value counterparts this week and over the last month, reflecting investor preference amid improving economic indicators.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><strong>Over the last month, small-, mid-, and large-cap growth equities experienced a rally vs. value equities</strong></p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_74c57fdcef7902d2590e033ab2f80650.png\" alt=\"US Equity Russell Indexes\" contenteditable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span>Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure></p> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Crypto \u2013 Bitcoin Crosses $100K</h2> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4364445-bitcoin-crosses-100000-as-trump-picks-crypto-backer-paul-atkins-for-sec-chair-powell-comments\">crossed the $100,000 threshold</a> for the first time on Tuesday evening, reaching a significant milestone. The price continued to climb, and by the morning of December 5th, the cryptocurrency was trading above the $100K mark. The milestone was driven by several factors, including optimism surrounding the incoming Trump administration\u2019s crypto-friendly policies and the nomination of crypto enthusiast Paul Atkins as the next SEC chairman. Other cryptocurrencies also reached new heights, with Ethereum reaching an <a href=\"https://www.financemagnates.com/cryptocurrency/why-is-ethereum-going-up-unpacking-eths-2024-price-surge-and-10000-predictions/\" rel=\"nofollow\">intraday high</a> of $3,908 on December 5th.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_6084c99a09e3b72636a6a2556b099d49.png\" alt=\"BTC vs. S&amp;P vs. DXY vs. 2YR Treasury\" contenteditable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span>TradingView, Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure></p> <h3 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Credit Conditions Continue Easing, Supporting Crypto</h3> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Increasingly looser financial conditions continue to amplify the rally in cryptocurrencies. The Chicago Fed\u2019s National Financial Conditions Index (NFCI) touched -0.63 for the week ending November 29, a new low for 2024 and the loosest in 3 years.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">NFCI is composed of risk, credit, and leverage. Deeper negative readings suggest that liquidity is improving relative to historical averages. This creates increasingly favorable environments for high-risk assets, such as Bitcoin.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <span><a href=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_76b569b7f879c18441fe170f8130dee4.png\" rel=\"lightbox\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"961\" data-og-image-twitter_small_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_large_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_image_post=\"true\" data-og-image-msn=\"true\" data-og-image-facebook=\"true\" data-og-image-google_news=\"true\" data-og-image-google_plus=\"true\" data-og-image-linkedin=\"true\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_76b569b7f879c18441fe170f8130dee4_thumb1.png\" alt=\"BTC vs. US Financial Conditions\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></span> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span>TradingView, Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure></p> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Currency &amp; Gold Performance</h2> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">The US Dollar Index (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DXY\" title=\"US Dollar Index\">DXY</a>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4353535-dollar-rises-amid-trumps-tariff-threats-euro-weakens-on-frances-political-turmoil-currency-recap\">strengthened significantly</a> early in the week, primarily driven by President-elect Donald Trump\u2019s threats to levy tariffs against BRICS nations over de-dollarization efforts, while the euro weakened against the dollar due to concerns about a potential French government collapse. Growing anticipation that the Bank of Japan (BOJ) will raise interest rates in December helped push the yen higher on a trailing one-month basis.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><strong>USD has outperformed the majority of currencies over the last month and YTD</strong></p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_015324c6f968508884c2397d5291b34b.png\" alt=\"USD vs. Major Currencies\" contenteditable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span>Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure></p> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Chart of the Week</h2> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">While Bitcoin has soared, gold hasn\u2019t shared the same fortune. Since late October, Bitcoin (BTC/USD) has jumped ~30%, while gold (XAU/USD) has dropped by ~5%.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">A stronger US dollar and rising Treasury yields are likely behind gold\u2019s struggles. As a non-yielding asset, gold often serves as a hedge against fiat currencies like the dollar.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Looking at quarterly data since 2000, the combined average of the US dollar and 10-year Treasury yield explains about 31% of gold\u2019s price movements. On their own, the US dollar explains 21%, and Treasury yields just 13%.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">If the Federal Reserve continues cutting interest rates, lower yields and a weaker dollar could give gold some much-needed support.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <span><a href=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_a2e9011857ca7c1544e2efeb1b4b0fcb.png\" rel=\"lightbox\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1062\" data-og-image-twitter_small_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_large_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_image_post=\"true\" data-og-image-msn=\"true\" data-og-image-facebook=\"true\" data-og-image-google_news=\"true\" data-og-image-google_plus=\"true\" data-og-image-linkedin=\"true\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_a2e9011857ca7c1544e2efeb1b4b0fcb_thumb1.png\" alt=\"Gold vs. Dollar + Treasuries\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></span> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span></span>TradingView, Seeking Alpha</p></figcaption></figure></p> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"> </h2> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Alpha Picks</h2> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/alpha-picks/about\">What is Alpha Picks?</a> Alpha Picks provides you with two data-driven stock picks a month delivered straight to your inbox. Alpha Picks has collectively gained 191%*, compared to the S&amp;P 500\u2019s 61%.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/alpha-picks/about\">What has Alpha Picks done lately?</a> All stocks in the Alpha Picks portfolio have now reported Q3 earnings, completing this quarter\u2019s earnings season. 29 out of 36 Alpha Picks exceeded earnings expectations in Q3, with 27 beating revenue targets, and 23 beating both top- and bottom-line consensus estimates. In just the past week, three Alpha Picks have delivered double-digit returns, led by Zeta Global Holdings Corp. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZETA\" title=\"Zeta Global Holdings Corp.\">ZETA</a>) with 28%, followed by AppLovin Corporation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/APP\" title=\"AppLovin Corporation\">APP</a>) with 15%, and Celestica Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CLS\" title=\"Celestica Inc.\">CLS</a>) with 11%.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <span><a href=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_a295b7fb3c9d371aec1e1debabe8be0e.png\" rel=\"lightbox\" data-width=\"1563\" data-height=\"882\" data-og-image-twitter_small_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_large_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_image_post=\"true\" data-og-image-msn=\"true\" data-og-image-facebook=\"true\" data-og-image-google_news=\"true\" data-og-image-google_plus=\"true\" data-og-image-linkedin=\"true\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_a295b7fb3c9d371aec1e1debabe8be0e_thumb1.png\" alt=\"Alpha Picks' Performance\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></span> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span>Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure></p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Above are some highlights regarding Alpha Picks' performance.</p> <h2 class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">Economic Rundown</h2> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">\u25ba FOMC \u2013 Traders are currently pricing in an 87% probability of a 25bps rate cut at the upcoming FOMC meeting on December 18th, following the 25bps cut in November. The November CPI Release next week will play a key role in determining the direction of rate cuts.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">\u25ba Inflation \u2013 As of October, inflation rates have shown signs of stabilization, with the annual rate at 2.6%. However, Fed officials remain vigilant about inflation trends and remain cautious about lowering interest rates.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\">\u25ba Labor Market \u2013 The November Jobs Report was strong; the economy added 227,000 jobs in November, bouncing back from October\u2019s disruptions caused by storms and strikes, while the employment rate ticked slightly higher to 4.2%.</p> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><strong><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar\">Seeking Alpha Earnings Calendar</a></strong></p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder paywall-full-content invisible\"></div> <p class=\"paywall-full-content invisible\"><figure class=\"regular-img-figure paywall-full-content invisible\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/6/saupload_69351096d449bd4178cc346d1eecb0de.png\" alt=\"Earnings Calendar\" contenteditable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"><span>Seeking Alpha</span></p></figcaption></figure></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691487492/image_1691487492.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742678-alpha-picks-weekly-market-recap", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 13:00:00"}]}